data.description: Build in 2021 3 bedroom/2.5 bathroom + LOFT home in prestigious Epperson Community. Warm and welcoming, this well-appointed home boasts plenty of living space, Updated to tile all first floor. A large GREAT ROOM, and BONUS LOFT. The SPACIOUS GOURMET kitchen is equipped with STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, closet pantry, QUARTZ countertops, and ISLAND with BREAKFAST BAR. The master suite includes a luxurious en suite bath with dual sinks and spacious walk-in shower. This home also includes two additional bedrooms, both bright and offering ample space. Sliding glass doors off the kitchen lead to your INCREDIBLE OUTDOOR LIVING SPACE! Newly Added an Oversized PAVER PATIO space and gorgeous outside ENTERTAINMENT CABANA. CUSTOM OUTDOOR KITCHEN boasting expansive grill, stainless steel appliances, & space for a large LCD TV. Fire pit for a Florida living at its finest! Ideal for family and entertaining! Epperson Community offers fantastic amenities including: LAGOON with water park, a fitness center, tennis courts, park, pool, and more! Close to shopping, dining, nightlife, with easy access to USF, WORLD CLASS BEACHES, Tampa International Airport, and DOWNTOWN TAMPA! Don't miss an opportunity to live in this SPECTACULAR home!
